{"tid":781974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鐘乳石是怎樣形成的？","createTime":"2018-08-16T10:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T07:14:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"922f2b3e02f5ef65be5dfced60361f661f4d60cf","tid":781974,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:34:28.000Z","msg":"鐘乳石是怎樣形成的？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%92%9F%E4%B9%B3%E7%9F%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%2592%259F%25E4%25B9%25B3%25E7%259F%25B3&d=Pl9Y0NndIBa%2F5fkSG1v2xQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7e653e06\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%92%9F%E4%B9%B3%E7%9F%B3</a><br />\n<br />\n鐘乳石為岩溶生成物，是指碳酸鹽岩地區洞穴內，在漫長地質歷史中和特定地質條件下形成的鐘乳石、石筍、石柱等不同形態碳酸鈣沉澱物。鐘乳石是滴水石的一種。由於形成時間漫長，鐘乳石對遠古地質考察有着重要的研究價值。由鐘乳石形成的洞穴可稱之為鐘乳洞。"},{"pid":"29492098c8af86379d7f4fe3a502a45d6179659b","tid":781974,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:48:05.000Z","msg":"可唔可以拎嚟起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc53293ae3205f1c446075d68f261df762f45ec5","tid":781974,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T07:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180817/large/a0401b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180817%2Flarge%2Fa0401b.gif&h=02246ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■長期滲水令西九站隧道水管出現「鐘乳石」。"}]}